"{\"uid\": \"metro.co.uk-2024-08-09-katarina-johnson-thompson-finally-claims-first-olympic-medal-21396855\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"An emotionalKatarina Johnson-Thompsonsaid she was 'relieved' after the Team GB athlete finally claimed her first Olympic medal with silver in the heptathlon atParis2024.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 169, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Team GB athlete\", \"from\": 67, \"to\": 86}, {\"ngram\": \"her first Olympic medal\", \"from\": 103, \"to\": 126}, {\"ngram\": \"silver\", \"from\": 132, \"to\": 138}, {\"ngram\": \"the heptathlon\", \"from\": 142, \"to\": 156}, {\"ngram\": \"atParis2024\", \"from\": 157, \"to\": 168}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Johnson-Thompson narrowly missed out on gold to the three-time Olympic champion Nafi Thiam despite the Belgian all the way across the two-day event.\", \"from\": 171, \"to\": 319, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 251, \"end\": 255, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nafi_language\", \"score\": 0.9382360940984357, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Nafi\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nafi_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nafi_language\"}, {\"begin\": 274, \"end\": 281, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgians\", \"score\": 0.9515712076831201, \"rank\": 0.025580524422573955, \"text\": \"Belgian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgians\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Johnson-Thompson\", \"from\": 171, \"to\": 187}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 211, \"to\": 215}, {\"ngram\": \"the three-time Olympic champion\", \"from\": 219, \"to\": 250}, {\"ngram\": \"the two-day event\", \"from\": 301, \"to\": 318}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Brit needed to beat Thiam in the 800m by eight seconds and as KJT crossed the line in second the Belgian was a fair distance behind her.\", \"from\": 321, \"to\": 461, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 422, \"end\": 429, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgians\", \"score\": 0.9515712076831201, \"rank\": 0.025580524422573955, \"text\": \"Belgian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgians\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Brit\", \"from\": 321, \"to\": 329}, {\"ngram\": \"Thiam\", \"from\": 345, \"to\": 350}, {\"ngram\": \"the 800m\", \"from\": 354, \"to\": 362}, {\"ngram\": \"eight seconds\", \"from\": 366, \"to\": 379}, {\"ngram\": \"KJT\", \"from\": 387, \"to\": 390}, {\"ngram\": \"the line\", \"from\": 399, \"to\": 407}, {\"ngram\": \"a fair distance\", \"from\": 434, \"to\": 449}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, Thiam just got over the line, with a couple of seconds to spare to keep hold of her Olympic title.\", \"from\": 463, \"to\": 570, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Thiam\", \"from\": 472, \"to\": 477}, {\"ngram\": \"the line\", \"from\": 492, \"to\": 500}, {\"ngram\": \"a couple\", \"from\": 507, \"to\": 515}, {\"ngram\": \"seconds\", \"from\": 519, \"to\": 526}, {\"ngram\": \"hold\", \"from\": 544, \"to\": 548}, {\"ngram\": \"her Olympic title\", \"from\": 552, \"to\": 569}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 31-year-old, though, has won two World Championship golds and now can boast an Olympic silver on her fourth trip to the Games.\", \"from\": 572, \"to\": 702, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"two World Championship golds\", \"from\": 605, \"to\": 633}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympic silver\", \"from\": 652, \"to\": 669}, {\"ngram\": \"her fourth trip\", \"from\": 673, \"to\": 688}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 692, \"to\": 701}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I can not even describe the words but I am just so relieved and so happy that I have an Olympic medal to add to my collection,' she told the BBC.\", \"from\": 704, \"to\": 850, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 846, \"end\": 849, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\", \"score\": 0.9944626571467359, \"rank\": 0.0055501842767682556, \"text\": \"BBC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the words\", \"from\": 729, \"to\": 738}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympic medal\", \"from\": 790, \"to\": 806}, {\"ngram\": \"my collection\", \"from\": 817, \"to\": 830}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'It was the only one I did not have and it's been so hard getting back to this point.\", \"from\": 852, \"to\": 937, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this point\", \"from\": 926, \"to\": 936}]}, {\"sentence\": \"What a phenomenal effort from KJT \\u00f0\\u009f\\u00ab\\u00b6A sensational silver in Paris \\u00f0\\u009f\\u00a5\\u0088Nafi Thiam did enough to secure an historic third Olympic gold medal.#BBCOlympics#Paris2024#Olympicspic.twitter.com/vRfsac1dBC 'In the lead-up to these Games, all I have been saying is that's what I want, obviously I wanted a medal but I just wanted to have a chance at the start of the 800m and that's what I had.\", \"from\": 939, \"to\": 1326, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1001, \"end\": 1006, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999517087884, \"rank\": 4.829117648477685e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"What a phenomenal effort\", \"from\": 939, \"to\": 963}, {\"ngram\": \"KJT \\u00f0\\u009f\\u00ab\\u00b6A sensational silver\", \"from\": 969, \"to\": 997}, {\"ngram\": \"Thiam\", \"from\": 1016, \"to\": 1021}, {\"ngram\": \"vRfsac1dBC\", \"from\": 1127, \"to\": 1137}, {\"ngram\": \"the lead-up\", \"from\": 1142, \"to\": 1153}, {\"ngram\": \"these Games\", \"from\": 1157, \"to\": 1168}, {\"ngram\": \"a medal\", \"from\": 1235, \"to\": 1242}, {\"ngram\": \"a chance\", \"from\": 1269, \"to\": 1277}, {\"ngram\": \"the start\", \"from\": 1281, \"to\": 1290}, {\"ngram\": \"the 800m\", \"from\": 1294, \"to\": 1302}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'It was a very far-off chance - eight seconds - but that's what this sport is, it's about getting to this point and seeing whose got it at the end.'\", \"from\": 1328, \"to\": 1476, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a very far-off chance\", \"from\": 1336, \"to\": 1357}, {\"ngram\": \"eight seconds\", \"from\": 1360, \"to\": 1373}, {\"ngram\": \"this sport\", \"from\": 1392, \"to\": 1402}, {\"ngram\": \"this point\", \"from\": 1429, \"to\": 1439}, {\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 1467, \"to\": 1474}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Thiam has now won gold at the last threeOlympic Games, cementing the Belgian's place as one of her country's finest-ever athletes.\", \"from\": 1478, \"to\": 1608, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1547, \"end\": 1554, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgians\", \"score\": 0.9515712076831201, \"rank\": 0.025580524422573955, \"text\": \"Belgian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgians\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Thiam\", \"from\": 1478, \"to\": 1483}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 1496, \"to\": 1500}, {\"ngram\": \"the last threeOlympic Games\", \"from\": 1504, \"to\": 1531}, {\"ngram\": \"her country's finest-ever athletes\", \"from\": 1573, \"to\": 1607}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Gold medalist in 2000, Denise Lewis, said of Thiam: 'She's been incredible, because she's know the pressure that she'd be under to achieve this incredibly rare feat.\", \"from\": 1610, \"to\": 1775, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1633, \"end\": 1645, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Denise_Lewis\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Denise Lewis\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Denise_Lewis\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Denise_